    "sequenceIcons": [
      {
        "sequence": 1,
        "name": "Stained in Scorched Earth",
        "description": "- Each stack of <te href=130601>Crown of Wills</te> additionally increases Augusta's Crit. DMG by 15%. \n- The max stack of Crown of Wills is increased to 2.\n- Casting <color=Highlight>Intro Skill - Stride of Goldenflare</color> now grants <SapTag=2>1</SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=stack P=stacks SapTag=2} of Crown of Wills. \n- <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Undying Sunlight: Strike</color>, <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Undying Sunlight: Leap</color>, and <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Undying Sunlight: Plunge</color> are now immune to interruption.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Image/IconDevice/T_IconDevice_AogusitaM1_UI.webp"
      },
      {
        "sequence": 2,
        "name": "Cleansed in Crimson War",
        "description": "- <te href=130601>Crown of Wills</te> provides additional effects: Each stack increases Augusta's Crit. Rate by 20%.\n- For every 1% of Crit. Rate over 100%, Augusta gains 2% Crit. DMG increase, up to 100%.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Image/IconDevice/T_IconDevice_AogusitaM2_UI.webp"
      },
      {
        "sequence": 3,
        "name": "Forged in Rot and Ruin",
        "description": "The following skills have their DMG Multiplier increased by 25%: \n- <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Thunderoar: Backstep</color>, <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter - Thunderoar: Backstep</color>, <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Thunderoar: Spinslash</color>, <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Thunderoar: Uppercut</color>.\n- <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Undying Sunlight: Plunge</color>.\n- <color=Highlight>Resonance Liberation - Sublime is the Sun: Sunborne</color>, <color=Highlight>Resonance Liberation - Sublime is the Sun: Everbright Protector</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Image/IconDevice/T_IconDevice_AogusitaM3_UI.webp"
      },
      {
        "sequence": 4,
        "name": "Ascent in Sun and Glory",
        "description": "Casting <color=Highlight>Intro Skill - Stride of Goldenflare</color> increases the ATK of all Resonators in the team by 20% for 30s.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Image/IconDevice/T_IconDevice_AogusitaM4_UI.webp"
      },
      {
        "sequence": 5,
        "name": "Unshaken in Wrathful Tides",
        "description": "The Shield provided by <color=Highlight>Inherent Skill - Glory's Favor</color> is increased by 50%.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Image/IconDevice/T_IconDevice_AogusitaM5_UI.webp"
      },
      {
        "sequence": 6,
        "name": "Engraved in Radiant Light",
        "description": "- Augusta can now hold up to 4 stacks of <te href=130601>Crown of Wills</te>. \n- For every 1% of Crit. Rate over 150%, Augusta gains 2% Crit. DMG increase, up to 50%.\n- When Augusta performs <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Thunderoar: Spinslash</color> or <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Thunderoar: Uppercut</color>, she obtains <SapTag=5>2</SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=stack P=stacks SapTag=5} of Crown of Wills. Augusta can only obtain <SapTag=8>2</SapTag> {Cus:Sap,S=stack P=stacks SapTag=8} of Crown of Wills every 1s via <color=Highlight>Engraved in Radiant Light</color>. \n- While casting <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Thunderoar: Spinslash</color> or <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Thunderoar: Uppercut</color>, Thunder Rage is triggered at the spot, dealing two instances of <color=Thunder>Electro DMG</color>, with each instance equal to 100% of Augusta's ATK, considered as Heavy Attack DMG.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Image/IconDevice/T_IconDevice_AogusitaM6_UI.webp"
      }
    ],
