        "description": "The DMG Multiplier of Forte Circuit's <color=Highlight>Sweet Dream</color> is additionally increased by 150%. \nForte Circuit <color=Highlight>Perennial</color>: Within 15s after casting <color=Highlight>Ephemeral</color>, if Concerto Energy is full and <color=Highlight>Perennial</color> is not on cooldown, Resonance Skill is replaced with <color=Highlight>Perennial</color>.\nCasting <color=Highlight>Perennial</color> consumes 50 Concerto Energy and recovers 50 Crimson Pistils, dealing <color=Dark>Havoc DMG</color> equal to 100% of <color=Highlight>Ephemeral</color> DMG, considered Basic Attack DMG. This skill can be cast once every 25s.\nCamellya enters <color=Highlight><te href=850021>Budding Mode</te></color> after casting <color=Highlight>Perennial</color> and removes all Crimson Buds. The bonus DMG Multiplier granted by Forte Circuit's <color=Highlight>Sweet Dream</color> is increased to 250%.\nImmune to interruptions when casting <color=Highlight>Perennial</color>.",
