          "description": "When a Resonator in the team defeats a target marked by <color=Highlight><te href=150801>Unseen Snare</te></color>, the Cooldown of Chisa's Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Eye of Unraveling</color> is reset, triggered up to once every 3s.",
