    "skillIcons": {
      "normalAttack": {
        "name": "POW POW",
        "description": "<size=40><color=Title>Basic Attack</color></size>\nChixia fires up to 4 consecutive shots, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack</color></size>\nChixia enters the aiming state for a more powerful shot.\nThe aimed shot fired after charging finishes deals <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Mid-air Attack</color></size>\nChixia consumes STA to perform consecutive shots at the target in mid-air, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Dodge Counter</color></size>\nUse <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> after a successful <color=Highlight>Dodge</color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconNor/SP_IconNorGun.webp"
      },
      "resonanceSkill": {
        "name": "Whizzing Fight Spirit",
        "description": "Chixia unleashes a flurry of shots, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<color=Highlight>Whizzing Fight Spirit</color> has 2 initial charges.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconMaxiaofang/SP_IconMaxiaofangB1.webp"
      },
      "forteCircuit": {
        "name": "Heroic Bullets",
        "description": "<size=40><color=Title>Resonance Skill: DAKA DAKA!</color></size>\nHold Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Whizzing Fight Spirit</color> to enter <color=Highlight>DAKA DAKA!</color>. In this state:\n- Chixia continuously consumes \"Thermobaric Bullets\" to attack the target, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, considered as Resonance Skill DMG.\n- Tap <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> to cast <color=Highlight>Basic Attack 4</color>, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, considered as Basic Attack DMG. Then she exits the \"DAKA DAKA!\" state.\n- If 30 \"Thermobaric Bullets\" have been fired when <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> is activated, Chixia will cast Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Boom Boom</color> and exit \"DAKA DAKA!\" state.\n- Chixia exits the \"DAKA DAKA!\" state when all \"Thermobaric Bullets\" are consumed.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Resonance Skill: Boom Boom</color></size>\nDeal <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>, considered as Resonance Skill DMG.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Thermobaric Bullets</color></size>\nChixia can hold up to 60 \"Thermobaric Bullets\".\nInherent Skill <color=Highlight>Scorching Magazine</color> increases Max \"Thermobaric Bullets\" by 10.\nChixia obtains \"Thermobaric Bullets\" for every Normal Attack <color=Highlight>POW POW</color> on hit.\nChixia obtains \"Thermobaric Bullets\" upon casting Intro Skill <color=Highlight>Grand Entrance</color> and Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Whizzing Fight Spirit</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconMaxiaofang/SP_IconMaxiaofangY.webp"
      },
      "resonanceLiberation": {
        "name": "Blazing Flames",
        "description": "Chixia fires up fast shots at nearby enemies, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconMaxiaofang/SP_IconMaxiaofangC1.webp"
      },
      "introSkill": {
        "name": "Grand Entrance",
        "description": "Chixia makes a heroic entrance and fires rapidly with her dual pistols at the target, dealing <color=Fire>Fusion DMG</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconMaxiaofang/SP_IconMaxiaofangQTE.webp"
      }
    },
