        "description": "When casting <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Ascent of Malice</color>, each point of <color=Highlight><te href=120801>Afterflame</te></color> additionally grants 2% Crit. DMG to <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Seraphic Execution</color>, <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Flamewing Verdict</color>, <color=Highlight>Mid-air Attack - Hellsent Barrage</color>,  <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Ravage</color>, and <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter  - Purgatory Scourge</color>, up to 80%. This effect is removed upon exiting <color=Highlight><te href=120805>Demon Hypostasis</te></color>.\nWhile in <color=Highlight><te href=120805>Demon Hypostasis</te></color>, <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Seraphic Execution Stage 5</color>, <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Flamewing Verdict Stage 3</color>, and <color=Highlight>Mid-air Attack - Hellsent Barrage</color> are immune to interruption.",
