        "description": "<color=Highlight><te href=120805>Demon Hypostasis</te></color> becomes <color=Highlight><te href=120806>Eternal Hypostasis</te></color>. <color=Highlight><te href=120806>Eternal Hypostasis</te></color> retains all effects of <color=Highlight><te href=120805>Demon Hypostasis</te></color>.\nAdditionally, <color=Highlight><te href=120806>Eternal Hypostasis</te></color> lasts, the DMG Multipliers of <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Seraphic Execution</color>, <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Flamewing Verdict</color>,  <color=Highlight>Mid-air Attack - Hellsent Barrage</color>, and <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter -Purgatory Scourge</color> are additionally increased by 60%.\n<size=10></size>\nWhen casting <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Ascent of Malice</color>, for every 1 point of <color=Highlight><te href=120801>Afterflame</te></color> consumed, Galbrena's <color=Highlight>Basic Attack - Seraphic Execution</color>, <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack - Flamewing Verdict</color>, <color=Highlight>Mid-air Attack - Hellsent Barrage</color>, <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill - Ravage</color>, and <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter -Purgatory Scourge</color> gain 0.875% Fusion DMG Amplification, up to 35%, which is removed upon exiting <color=Highlight><te href=120806>Eternal Hypostasis</te></color>.",
