        "name": "Rage Transposition",
        "description": "The incoming Resonator gains 38% Heavy Attack DMG Amplification for 14s or until they are switched out.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconMotefei/SP_IconMotefeiT.webp"
