    "skillIcons": {
      "normalAttack": {
        "name": "Vibration Manifestation",
        "description": "<size=40><color=Title>Basic Attack</color></size>\nRover performs up to 4 consecutive attacks, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack</color></size>\nRover consumes STA to attack the target, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack: Resonance</color></size>\nAfter <color=Highlight>Basic Attack 3</color> or <color=Highlight>Heavy Attack</color>, press the <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> button at the right time to perform Heavy Attack <color=Highlight>Resonance</color>, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Heavy Attack: Aftertune</color></size>\nAfter Heavy Attack <color=Highlight>Resonance</color> or <color=Highlight>Dodge Counter</color> hits a target, press the <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> button to perform Heavy Attack <color=Highlight>Aftertune</color>, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Mid-air Attack</color></size>\nRover consumes STA to perform a Mid-Air Plunging Attack, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Dodge Counter</color></size>\nUse <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> after a successful <color=Highlight>Dodge</color> to attack the target, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconNor/SP_IconNorKnife.webp"
      },
      "resonanceSkill": {
        "name": "Resonating Slashes",
        "description": "Rover launches an attack forward, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconZhujue/SP_IconZhujueB1.webp"
      },
      "forteCircuit": {
        "name": "World in a Grain of Sand",
        "description": "<size=40><color=Title>Resonance Skill: Resonating Spin</color></size>\nIf \"Diminutive Sound\" exceeds 50 when <color=Highlight>Resonance Skill</color> is used, consume 50 \"Diminutive Sound\" to cast <color=Highlight>Resonating Spin</color>, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>. This DMG is considered as Resonance Skill DMG and applies 2 stack(s) of <color=Highlight><te href=850008>Spectro Frazzle</te></color> along with <color=Highlight>Shimmer</color>.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Shimmer</color></size>\n<color=Highlight>Shimmer</color> prevents <color=Highlight><te href=850008>Spectro Frazzle</te></color> stacks from reducing over time.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Basic Attack: Resonating Echoes</color></size>\nAfter Resonance Skill <color=Highlight>Resonating Spin</color> ends, follow up with <color=Highlight>Basic Attack</color> to cast <color=Highlight>Resonating Echoes</color>.\nLaunch forward to attack the enemies, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>, considered as Resonance Skill DMG.\n<size=10> </size>\n<size=40><color=Title>Diminutive Sound</color></size>\nRover can hold up to 100 \"Diminutive Sounds\".\nRover obtains \"Diminutive Sound\" for every Normal Attack <color=Highlight>Vibration Manifestation</color> on hit. \nRover obtains \"Diminutive Sound\" for every Heavy Attack <color=Highlight> Aftertune</color> on hit.\nRover obtains \"Diminutive Sound\" upon casting Intro Skill <color=Highlight>Waveshock</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconZhujue/SP_IconZhujueY.webp"
      },
      "resonanceLiberation": {
        "name": "Echoing Orchestra",
        "description": "Channel Spectro energy to attack the target area, causing a blast after a short delay, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color> and applying 6 stack(s) of <color=Highlight><te href=850008>Spectro Frazzle</te></color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconZhujue/SP_IconZhujueC1.webp"
      },
      "introSkill": {
        "name": "Waveshock",
        "description": "Rover attacks the target, dealing <color=Light>Spectro DMG</color>.",
        "iconSourceUrl": "https://static.nanoka.cc/assets/ww/UIResources/Common/Atlas/SkillIcon/SkillIconZhujue/SP_IconZhujueQTE.webp"
      }
    },
